    {
      "id": "dmf-goal",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Thesis",
      "position": {
        "x": -40,
        "y": -320
      },
      "width": 660,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Domain Memory Factory (Agents)\n**Thesis:** long-running agents fail when they are *amnesiac*. The fix is not a smarter model — it’s **durable domain memory** + a **harness ritual** that forces disciplined progress.\n\nTwilite turns domain memory into a shareable artifact: a persistent `.node` graph that evolves by validated deltas.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
